Q) Command to run created emulator from cmd :-
A) Go to platformtools folder and run command "emulator -avd <Emulator_Name>"

Note :- npm is a command line used to download all node module.

Add NodeJS home and npn/bin in PATH variable.

You can download any node module using npm.

Command to install Appium usimg npm "npm install -g appium"
Always give us stable version

Run "appium" command toi run appium on your machine

To uninstall appium "npm uninstall -g appium"

To install any specific version
"npn install -g appium@beta --no-shrinkwrap"








